metadata.name: #1 Tickets for use of the Human Generation Lab
metadata.description:
Purchase this lab ticket to generate your own special existence!　Just prepare the 6 elements you want to add to your character!　Together we will create an isolated inhabitant of an artificial paradise!
Contents
Size 6000 x 8000 One frontal character standing picture
Size 2000x2000 One character icon
Mint at aono chan's experimental lab

After confirming the elements, we will begin production.
Confirmation will be taken once at the draft stage.
Generated characters can be used for commercial purposes, and can be used for any purpose!

See the Description of the collection.
Please DM gesyutaruto after purchase.
Please link your Twitter account with FOUNDATION.
